id.docs:
**[ID](https://esphome.io/guides/configuration-types.html#config-id)**: The id to use for this tlc59208f component. Use this if you have multiple TLC59208Fs connected at the same time



*See also: [Component](https://esphome.io/components/output/tlc59208f.html#configuration-variables)*

address.docs:
**int**: The I²C address of the driver. Defaults to `0x20`.



*See also: [Component](https://esphome.io/components/output/tlc59208f.html#configuration-variables)*
